_sText:
A Skiing map where you have fun going down the hill and can collect your weapons to kill the enemies. Bomb site at the ski lodge at the bottom of the hill, and chair lift teleports back up to the top. Get air skiing by surfing sideways then quickly turning off of the slope. Lots of fun. (if you cant see your crosshair make it translucent)

Set for up to 32 spawns
